obuild-ver: 1
Name: vg
Synopsis: Declarative 2D vector graphics for OCaml
Version: repo
Authors: Daniel BÃ¼nzli <daniel.buenzli at erratique.ch>
License: BSD3
Homepage: http://erratique.ch/software/vg
Description:
 Vg is a library for declarative 2D vector graphics. The render
 backend is open and built-in support for rendering to PDF, SVG and
 the HTML5 canvas element is provided.
 .
 Vg depends on [Gg][1] and is distributed under the BSD3 license.
 .
 [1]: http://erratique.ch/software/gg

Flag jsoo
 Description: build js_of_ocaml support
 Default: true

Library vg
 Modules: Vg, Vgr_pdf, Vgr_svg
 Path: src
 BuildDepends: gg

 Library jsoo
  Path: src
  Modules: Vgr_jsoo
  Buildable: $jsoo
  BuildDepends: js_of_ocaml, js_of_ocaml.syntax
  pp: camlp4o

Test vgtest
  Path: vgtest
  MainIs: vg_test.ml
  